<div class="about-me box-white">
  <div class="about inner">
    <div class="section-about-me">
      <h3 class="section-title">About me</h3>
      <p class="section-description">
        I moved to from Boston to IL in search of a NEW adventure and a NEW challenge after finishing up
        my degree in Computer Science and Psychology. I quickly found my way to Tel Aviv where I enjoy the
        very hot summers and suffer through the cold winters.
      </p>
      <p class="section-description">
        I love to build, to learn, and to ask questions. I ask an inordinate amount of questions in order to understand the full
        picture of the tech I work on. For me, it is not enough to submit code that works- I must refactor until it is great!
      </p>
    </div>
      <img class="about-me-img" src="images/mesquare.png">
  </div>
</div>
<div class="contact box-full">
  <div class="contact-info inner">
    <h3 class="section-title">Contact Me</h3>
